    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds nice in a poem or something but it doesnt feel real. it feels like just another way to lie to yourself so you dont have to face the fact that everything is going to end badly. how can you say my life is the only thing that matters when the entire context for my life—the environment, the future, the climate—is becoming uninhabitable? it feels like building a sandcastle right before a massive wave hits. why bother?",
